scene.message:
Maki: This city's not so{nl}
bad, right? I think{nl}
paradise is a place like this.{waitkey}It's ordinary, but{nl}
every day is fun.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That person Kurouri{nl}
mentioned has me{nl}
curious...{waitkey}{clearbox}{ctl0f:1},{nl}
don't forget to visit{nl}
the Araya Shrine.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: This place is just{nl}
like our city...{nl}
smells all musty.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: So this is the{nl}
Mirror of Harming.{nl}
So mysterious and lovely!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: So this is the{nl}
Mirror of Harming...{wait_fr:37}{nl}
Let's see if it shows{nl}
this handsome face.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: The Mirror of{nl}
Harming? Will it show{nl}
Ayase's face? My skin's{nl}
been rough lately, sigh...{waitkey}{ret}

The Mirror of Harming{nl}
gives off a divine,{nl}
holy aura...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Found it!{nl}
This is the Mirror of{nl}
Harming, isn't it!{waitkey}{ret}

You mustn't take this...{nl}
You really mustn't...{nl}
You mustn'ttttt...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What was that just{nl}
now...! It looked like{nl}
a little girl's face.{waitkey}She said not to take 'this'...{waitkey}{clearbox}Did she mean the{nl}
Mirror of Harming?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Who cares about that!{nl}
We're in trouble{nl}
without this thing.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: That face just now...{nl}
it looked like{nl}
little Mai...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Here, {ctl0f:1}.{nl}
With this, we can fight{nl}
that monster in the{nl}
subway, right?{waitkey}{ret}
